				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "\n\nAutomated testing is important",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a5ff6c001r5iZGLqgGg8Dzs"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " for software quality because it provides fast, repeatable verification that code behaves as expected after",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a5ff6c001r5iZGLqgGg8Dzs"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " every change. Manual testing is slow, error-prone, and doesn't scale — a",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a5ff6c001r5iZGLqgGg8Dzs"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " human can't reliably re-check thousands of behaviors across a",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a5ff6c001r5iZGLqgGg8Dzs"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " codebase after each commit. Automated tests catch regressions early, before they reach production, and serve as executable documentation",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a5ff6c001r5iZGLqgGg8Dzs"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " of intended behavior. They enable developers to refactor with confidence, knowing that breaking changes will surface immediately rather",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a5ff6c001r5iZGLqgGg8Dzs"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " than weeks later in a bug report. Over time, a well-maintained",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a5ff6c001r5iZGLqgGg8Dzs"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": " test suite reduces the cost of change, shortens feedback loops, and shifts quality ass",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a5ff6c001r5iZGLqgGg8Dzs"
				},
				{
					"type": "delta",
					"text": "urance from a reactive gate at the end of development to a continuous, integrated part of the workflow.",
					"messageId": "msg_d28a5ff6c001r5iZGLqgGg8Dzs"
				},
